OL,6,FThe unusual referral followed an
OL,7,Fexclusive investigation by ITV News
OL,8,Finto extreme customer service failures
OL,9,Fby the UK's biggest energy supplier.
OL,11,FThe Information Commissioner confirmed
OL,12,Fit had received a report from British
OL,13,FGas following an incident where credit
OL,14,Freference agencies were erroneously
OL,15,Finformed of non-payment of a debt.
OL,17,FThe 'incident' refers to their
OL,18,Freporting of missed payments against
OL,19,Fthe credit record of Alison Greenough.
