OL,3,CCustomers fight British Gas billing
OL,4,Cerrors - how to check your credit score
OL,6,FThe now-former British Gas customer
OL,7,Fwas preparing to remortgage her family
OL,8,Fhome in January when she discovered
OL,9,Fher excellent credit score had been
OL,10,Fdemolished by problems with a British
OL,11,FGas direct debit.
OL,13,FAlison had to accept a loan with far
OL,14,Fhigher repayments, costing her more
OL,15,Fthan #7,000.
OL,17,FSince ITV News' investigation, Alison
OL,18,Fhas successfully taken her complaint
OL,19,Fagainst British Gas to the small
OL,20,Fclaims court.
