OL,6,FShe was rewarded #7,363 compensation
OL,7,Ffrom the energy giant, who accepted
OL,8,Fresponsibility. Catherine O'Kelly, the
OL,9,FManaging Director of British Gas,
OL,10,Fcalled Allison to personally apologise
OL,11,Ffor the experience.
OL,13,FAlison says the energy firm put her
OL,14,Ffamily through "months and months of
OL,15,Fhell", but she is hopeful her case can
OL,16,Finspire others who may have a similar
OL,17,Fexperience.
