OL,6,FThey were rejected due to missed
OL,7,Fpayments for a British Gas electricity
OL,8,Faccount amounting to #1,000 ` despite
OL,9,Fbeing customers with another provider.
OL,10,FLiam then discovered the missed
OL,11,Fpayments were actually for his
OL,12,Fneighbour's consumption. He
OL,13,Fimmediately disputed the case.
OL,15,FLiam told ITV News that despite
OL,16,Fcountless calls to British Gas,
OL,17,Fcustomer service agents were unable to
OL,18,Fresolve his issue.
