OL,6,F"You see adverts saying, 'We pride
OL,7,Fourselves on customer service'... but
OL,8,Fthis is the reality. This is what I'm
OL,9,Fleft with and what I have to clean up
OL,10,Ffor them."
OL,12,FAfter ITV News contacted British Gas
OL,13,Fover Liam's case, they were able to
OL,14,Fremove the incorrect marks against
OL,15,FLiam's credit record and the mortgage
OL,16,Fhas now been approved.
