OL,12,Fher former address ` despite having
OL,13,Fcontacted the firm before she moved.
OL,14,FElaye too found customer service
OL,15,Fagents were unable to help her, so
OL,16,Fcontacted the Energy Ombudsman and
OL,17,Feventually her credit file was
OL,18,Fcorrected.
