OL,6,F"No mortgage provider would lend to me
OL,7,Fbecause of these defaults, I am too
OL,8,Fhigh risk. Everything I had worked for
OL,9,Fup until that point ` gone."
OL,11,FBritish Gas concedes it posted Elaye's
OL,12,Fbill to the wrong address - though it
OL,13,Fsays it also sent bills online and via
OL,14,Femails.
OL,16,FAcknowledging its errors, the energy
OL,17,Ffirm sent Elaye a #100 compensation
OL,18,Fcheque. But just like her previous
OL,19,Fbills - it was sent to the wrong
OL,20,Faddress.
