OL,3,CCustomers fight British Gas billing
OL,4,Cerrors - how to check your credit score
OL,6,FLike most big firms, British Gas
OL,7,Fshares information with credit
OL,8,Freference agencies. They compile
OL,9,Ffinancial reports, known as credit
OL,10,Fscores, that lenders check. However,
OL,11,Fthe wrong information can end up with
OL,12,Fyou getting the wrong credit score.
OL,14,FThe accuracy of the credit score you
OL,15,Fget relies on the information these
OL,16,Fagencies get. And British Gas isn't
OL,17,Fthe only firm that makes mistakes.
OL,18,FConsumer group Which? found a third of
OL,19,Fpeople who checked their credit
OL,20,Freports discovered an error caused by
OL,21,Fa wide range of firms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
