OL,6,FIf you have been experiencing issues
OL,7,Fwith your Energy Provider, we want to
OL,8,Fhear your story. Get in touch with the
OL,9,Fteam at: consumerteam@itv.com
OL,11,FJohn Webb, Senior Consumer Affairs
OL,12,FManager at Experian told ITV News that
OL,13,Ferrors on credit reports are
OL,14,F"extremely rare" - but the onus should
OL,15,Fbe on the company providing data to
OL,16,Fensure it is correct, not their
OL,17,Fcustomer.
