OL,6,FThough all of the energy customers ITV
OL,7,FNews has spoken to say the
OL,8,Fresponsibility fell on them to try and
OL,9,Fnavigate the British Gas customer
OL,10,Fservice system, and they did not know
OL,11,Fthe credit agencies could dispute any
OL,12,Fissues on their behalf.
OL,14,FWhat should you do if you are
OL,15,Fconcerned about incorrect defaults on
OL,16,Fyour account?
OL,18,FExperian says the first thing anyone
OL,19,Fshould do is check their free
OL,20,Fstatutory credit report, which is
OL,21,Favailable from all credit agencies.
