OL,3,CCustomers fight British Gas billing
OL,4,Cerrors - how to check your credit score
OL,6,FThey suggest you do this at least once
OL,7,Fa year, but especially before applying
OL,8,Ffor any new credit or accounts.
OL,10,FIf something on the report doesn't
OL,11,Flook right, report it to your credit
OL,12,Fagency. They will then provide support
OL,13,Fthroughout a dispute process ` which
OL,14,Fincludes adding a note against the
OL,15,Faccount to advise other lenders it is
OL,16,Fbeing investigated.
