OL,6,FITV News contacted British Gas over
OL,7,Fcomplaints of unfairly damaged scores.
OL,8,FThey told us in a statement: "When we
OL,9,Fmake mistakes, we hold our hands up,
OL,10,Fwe make it right and we learn from
OL,11,Fthem because we care about our service
OL,12,Fand we care about our customers. These
OL,13,Fwere unconnected cases, where some
OL,14,Faspects were beyond our control but
OL,15,Fwhere we made mistakes, we're sorry
OL,16,Ffor that. We'll learn from these
OL,17,Fisolated cases to continue to improve
OL,18,Four customer service."
